{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And 20 years later, I still was left with the same impression that I should be an engineer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It turned out that the war, exposure to different cultures, traveling-- I developed an excellent ability to learn languages.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And actually, I-- whenever I went to a country or was there, I could acquire the language very quickly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was pretty good at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I certainly developed an ability to learn, whether it's English or whether it was Czechish or whether it was-- well, certainly Hebrew, I knew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I was pretty good at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I can write very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so apparently talents or abilities change, either with age or with circumstances or both.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But anyway, this is how I was scheduled to be an engineer in those days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was not very athletic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I probably suffered like every other child, since I observe mine, from the peer pressure and cruelty of a mob psychology that exists between children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the Jewish-- mind you, one thing that my father made sure, and-- that I was going to a Hebrew high school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even though I was very well-versed in Polish literature and in Polish intellectual life and I certainly spoke the language very well-- and there was no question about it, I was certainly saved from any of the cruelties of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is no doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I was aware of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you could hear it or you could see it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I personally as a child never suffered from it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever I went to resorts, it was a lot of populated by Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I went to countryside-- when I was at school, it was a Hebrew high school.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
